        <p class="intro" style="margin-top:1em;"><dfn id="frenquencies_def">Frequencies</dfn> show the percentage of Numista users who own each year or variety among all the users who own this coin. Since some users own several versions, the sum may be greater than 100%.</p>
        
</section>

        


